*''The High Renaissance and Mannerism''. London: Thames & Hudson, 1967. (with Linda Murray)
*[[Jacob Burckhardt|Burckhardt, Jacob]]. ''The architecture of the Italian Renaissance''. Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 1985. (Revised and edited)

